RACE.FOOTNOTES: TROTTING GEAR tracked the early leader two deep, took command through the upper stretch and drew off to be well clear late under steady pressure. SUBTLE FAITH rated along under a hold early on, moved up along the inside through the far turn, shifted out to race four deep through the stretch and got up for the place position. MOON ROSE stalked the top pair from the outside, moved up five wide to take aim near the three sixteenths pole and flattened out. SECRET OF SARATOGA showed good early foot to set the early pace along the inside and gave way in the drive. QUICKSTYLE was off slowly, raced three to four wide through the stretch and never threatened. SHILOH was off a step slow, coaxed along early and lacked a bid. SHOW ME LOVE dropped back early on, lost ground to race far back and was eased up on in the stretch.
